''shoonen yo shinwa ni nare''

7
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:29,100
''aoi kaze ga ima mune no DOOR wo tataitemo''

8
00:00:29,100 --> 00:00:37,200
''watashidake wo tada mitsumete hohoenderu anata''

9
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:44,000
''sotto fureru mono motomeru koto ni muchuude''

10
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:50,700
''unmei sae mada shiranai itaike na hitomi''

11
00:00:51,700 --> 00:00:57,800
''dakedo itsuka kizuku deshou sono senaka niwa''

12
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:05,800
''haruka mirai mezasu tame no hane ga aru koto''

13
